  "title": "Robustly Aromatic Malaysian Chicken Curry",
  "description": "A funky and shattering monsoon Malaysian dish featuring unwaxed lemon and mushimono-steam, this flexitarian-friendly curry is perfect for a weeknight dinner. It combines the flavors of Malaysia with a unique twist.",
