  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add chicken and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add curry powder and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add coconut milk and lemon juice, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
